WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:02.286
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:02.286 --> 00:00:05.200
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:09.611
It's Brandon and Diana, the Dynamic Duo.

00:00:09.611 --> 00:00:13.440
We're here and we're ready to pray.

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:19.543
We've been seeking the Lord today and praying over our nation because of all that happened today.

00:00:19.829 --> 00:00:24.755
The Lord has been warning us that this was going to take place.

00:00:25.573 --> 00:00:31.360
We pray for the troops, the two victims who are fighting for their lives right now.

00:00:31.360 --> 00:00:38.160
I don't know if they're still alive or still fighting, but we know that God is able, and we're going to pray for them right now.

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:48.749
We're going to pray for their families and pray peace over them, that God would restore their health and that this heinous act will be punished quickly.

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:57.004
What the devil meant for bad, God's going to turn around and get the glory for it.

00:00:57.342 --> 00:01:01.360
I believe with all my heart that's what we're here for.

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:07.920
As I was praying this afternoon, I was caught up.

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:13.946
He spoke about Saturday; we were praying over Saturday and the 14 people.

00:01:13.946 --> 00:01:20.400
There are other events, and the Lord said, 'This is what I warned you about.

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:23.840
These are the things that I'm warning you about.

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:28.960
' It's underground chatter, and the Lord specifically brought this up today.

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:35.200
He said, 'The underground chatter, son, for more acts to come.

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:50.171
' We are praying against the acts to come over our malls specifically, and the tree-lighting ceremonies and drones.

00:01:50.171 --> 00:01:57.394
They have brought forth this one act, and you'll hear in just a second more about what's going to happen because of the act that happened today.

00:02:06.533 --> 00:02:07.726
We pray.

00:02:07.726 --> 00:02:13.955
This was right by the White House, and President Trump wasn't there, thank God.

00:02:13.955 --> 00:02:19.799
He was at Mar-a-Lago, and we continued to pray for him and for Vice President Vance.

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:36.549
I keep forgetting; you'll have to bear with me.

00:02:36.549 --> 00:02:38.740
We pray for JD Vance.

00:02:38.740 --> 00:02:58.596
I know what the Lord is warning me about, and he keeps bringing up that in the days ahead, they will challenge the peace that you have every single day as you go about your normal life.

00:03:04.709 --> 00:03:09.519
The enemy would try to challenge that so you live in fear and question everything: 'Is it okay to go here?

00:03:09.519 --> 00:03:12.976
Is it okay to go there?

00:03:12.976 --> 00:03:24.560
' We take for granted as United States citizens the great job our law enforcement does every single day.

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:34.799
Our FBI, our Homeland Security, our local law enforcement, and our sheriff's departments are always out to protect and serve our beautiful nation.

00:03:35.759 --> 00:03:49.267
The enemy would try to challenge our way of life so that you would feel that insecurity of whether we are safe to go to the mall.

00:04:14.170 --> 00:04:14.540
That was what the Lord was showing me: the enemy was going to try to instill fear, worry, panic, and dread.

00:04:14.540 --> 00:04:31.160
As I was praying over that today, I kept praying into Saturday tree-lighting ceremonies and massive get-togethers tomorrow for the parade, praying over New York, Las Vegas, our airports, our TSA, and those who check the baggage.

00:04:31.160 --> 00:04:38.699
We pray that God would always intervene, that there would be supernatural divine intervention for our nation.

00:04:38.699 --> 00:04:42.240
That's what we'll continue to pray about tonight.

00:04:46.571 --> 00:04:49.623
That is what I feel in my heart the Lord is wanting us to keep interceding for.

00:04:49.623 --> 00:04:53.350
Like I said, stuff like this shouldn't happen.

00:04:53.350 --> 00:04:59.577
The fact that two troops got almost fatally shot so far is ridiculous.

00:05:03.911 --> 00:05:08.310
I wanted to say everything is at peace, but we live in a fallen world and things sometimes slip through the cracks.

00:05:08.770 --> 00:05:12.937
We're going to stand on the blood and our covenant tonight, believing God for the holiday season.

00:05:20.035 --> 00:05:27.140
In particular, the Lord said Thursday, Friday, and Saturday are three major days.

00:05:28.010 --> 00:05:36.680
We have work to do, and I believe many people are up for the task.

00:05:36.680 --> 00:05:42.780
There are 2,000 of you here already; you know the seriousness of the hour.

00:05:43.530 --> 00:05:47.931
Some of you don't even live in America, but this was not concerning just America.

00:05:47.931 --> 00:05:54.839
The Lord said, 'You must pray for France, Germany, and all of Europe.

00:05:54.839 --> 00:05:59.268
' Praying for Australia, New Zealand, and so on.

00:06:00.331 --> 00:06:11.109
It's interesting—I didn't feel led to pray concerning these terrorist attacks for any Asian nations; it's always the Western nations like Europe and Canada.

00:06:22.567 --> 00:06:23.808
We'll just do our job.

00:06:24.056 --> 00:06:29.508
I want to play this video if you're not familiar with today's events.

00:06:37.449 --> 00:06:37.867
Pete is his name, Hegseth.

00:06:44.430 --> 00:06:55.320
They're going to bring out more troops, which isn't a coincidence, thank God, because of what I've seen concerning the tree-lighting ceremony.

00:06:56.960 --> 00:07:03.702
Whenever I've told you about the map with the Lego-like buildings, they were planning and strategizing against our nation's capital.

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:12.720
I saw these men, and it was for the underground chatter.

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:22.320
I keep seeing these secret networks of phone lines that are coded so they can talk without being interrupted.

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:33.160
I believe it's the same thing they had in New York that we discovered around September 21st.

00:07:36.091 --> 00:07:41.280
The Lord said Chicago, Seattle, and Boston have the same kind of networking as New York.

00:07:51.220 --> 00:07:56.149
We pray that those be uncovered and brought to light.

00:07:57.383 --> 00:08:08.863
The Lord said these are the same kind of SIM cards—a very well-funded thing to topple the eagle so that they are able to do what they want to do.

00:08:09.087 --> 00:08:20.879
They said, 'We must topple the eagle and bring havoc on the inside so we can do what we want with Israel and these other areas.

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:26.400
' As America goes, so does the world; we're the watchdogs of the world.

00:08:30.080 --> 00:08:39.840
Even now, the main vision I saw for 2025 was Trump coming on the scene in January and standing on a conductor's platform like a lion tamer, cracking his whip to the nations.

00:08:58.789 --> 00:09:03.280
I saw him crack his whip at the bear and the dragon, and they paused.

00:09:08.142 --> 00:09:17.589
He was bringing peace for a season, while others would try to escalate things and maneuver around his administration, waiting for his term to be over, even considering how they could eliminate him.

00:09:34.199 --> 00:09:48.959
And the Lord said, "We must pray for President Trump, not just for the physical, but for discernment on who he allows into his inner circle as nations would try to deceive him.

00:09:49.233 --> 00:09:59.519
" He said that he would have great discernment in the days ahead of how to handle doing business.

00:09:59.519 --> 00:10:00.411
"Don't trust everybody.

00:10:00.411 --> 00:10:05.120
" And the Lord said he needs to work on discernment.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:08.587
Even then, don't just trust people blindly, sir.

00:10:08.587 --> 00:10:11.760
There are enemies; there are rats within.

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:15.839
And the Lord keeps telling me there's rats in the Pentagon.

00:10:15.839 --> 00:10:17.239
There's rats in the FBI.

00:10:17.239 --> 00:10:18.826
There's rats in Homeland Security.

00:10:18.826 --> 00:10:21.040
There's rats in these places.

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:25.680
And he said these people are leaking information.

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:26.280
He specifically told me this.

00:10:26.280 --> 00:10:31.860
Now, I don't know if you have found them all yet, but I have prayed continually that you will.

00:10:31.860 --> 00:10:37.387
I even saw in particular people—the Lord showed me these people are rats.

00:10:37.387 --> 00:10:41.440
You must pray for them to be exposed and brought to justice.

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:42.880
So that's been our prayer.

00:10:43.199 --> 00:10:44.540
As a family, we pray over that too.

00:10:44.540 --> 00:10:51.653
And we pray over President Trump continually—about his heart, about his veins—even before anything was brought up on the news.

00:10:51.653 --> 00:11:00.183
If you go back, we've been praying over his heart, his veins, and his mind for pressure from all the stress from the job.

00:11:00.183 --> 00:11:02.773
It's a majorly stressful job when you're doing what he's doing.

00:11:03.531 --> 00:11:05.640
So, we're praying for him and we continue to do that.

00:11:05.640 --> 00:11:15.291
I'm praying for his marriage, praying for his kids and his grandkids, for Kai in particular concerning Washington DC when she's there.

00:11:15.291 --> 00:11:18.149
Praying for her, a hedge around and about her.

00:11:18.149 --> 00:11:26.023
And so, I believe with all my heart our prayers have great traction in them and we're making progress.

00:11:26.023 --> 00:11:28.666
So, we're going to continue to do that.

00:11:29.253 --> 00:11:33.680
Let's go over a little bit of what happened last night.

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:45.520
If you were here for the almost three-hour video—I told Diana, I said, "Well, the squawkers will squawk, but I tell you, the glory was here, and I didn't want to cut it off.

00:11:46.719 --> 00:11:53.958
" I told her, I said, "When I was seeing over there and that angel came, that was beautiful.

00:11:54.479 --> 00:11:57.040
" When you have those experiences with the Father...

00:11:57.480 --> 00:11:58.610
She's been crying.

00:11:58.840 --> 00:12:01.608
I'm telling you, the glory of the Lord—we felt it today.

00:12:01.608 --> 00:12:06.960
And when the angel said to us, "I've been assigned to you.

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:08.400
I have been assigned.

00:12:08.400 --> 00:12:13.860
" Diana and I—Diana's a thinker—were just going over things: Is it Michael?

00:12:18.376 --> 00:12:18.674
Was that Michael?

00:12:19.268 --> 00:12:20.764
He didn't say his name.

00:12:20.764 --> 00:12:21.671
I don't know.

00:12:21.671 --> 00:12:23.720
But I believe he was an archangel.

00:12:23.720 --> 00:12:26.034
And he said, "I have been assigned to help you.

00:12:26.034 --> 00:12:26.776
I've been assigned.

00:12:26.776 --> 00:12:31.839
" And when he was standing there, I thought, "He is a fierce thing.

00:12:31.839 --> 00:12:35.863
" I mean, that angel looked awesome.

00:12:36.686 --> 00:12:38.520
I've described it to everyone.

00:12:39.420 --> 00:12:41.040
Braden made the shield.

00:12:42.160 --> 00:12:46.359
He tried to make the shield the way I described it the best he could.

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:53.943
It was his breastplate.

00:12:53.943 --> 00:12:59.240
He didn't have a shield; he had a sword in one hand and a horn in the other.

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:00.651
And I thought that was interesting.

00:13:00.651 --> 00:13:10.765
It looked like that, but it was turning like a galaxy—not a black hole, but like what you'd see in a Milky Way picture.

00:13:11.496 --> 00:13:17.040
It was turning like a circle inside of his chest.

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:19.573
It was moving; all that was alive.

00:13:19.573 --> 00:13:27.484
And as it was turning in him, his skin—what you would consider our skin—was opal.

00:13:27.484 --> 00:13:31.181
And he was turning and making different colors.

00:13:31.403 --> 00:13:38.104
He was like one of those kaleidoscopes—one of those little things you can look through—and that's the way his skin looked.

00:13:39.115 --> 00:13:44.040
His face kept changing and he was glistening and glowing.

00:13:45.920 --> 00:13:54.373
It was fascinating because the Lord allowed me to look; the portal was right here and it opened up and he just stood there.

00:13:54.747 --> 00:13:57.097
The Lord allowed me to keep looking at him.

00:13:57.097 --> 00:14:08.680
Usually the visions will change, but the Lord let me just see this angelic being right here, and that was amazing.

00:14:08.680 --> 00:14:12.480
No, it was not natural.

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:24.194
If you have that kind of encounter, you're on your face; the presence of the Lord, when an angelic being like that in physical form comes, is the glory of the Lord.

00:14:24.194 --> 00:14:29.982
But when you're seeing in spirit, it's filtered for me; you're able to stand it.

00:14:29.982 --> 00:14:38.959
But when I was looking at him, he kept looking back at me, but he was always keeping his face to the Father.

00:14:38.959 --> 00:14:41.211
He was looking to the Father.

00:14:41.211 --> 00:14:49.760
He would glance at us, but he would look at the Father and he kept his eyes to the Father the whole time.

00:14:51.1000 --> 00:14:53.199
It was amazing.

00:14:53.199 --> 00:14:57.611
He wasn't looking around for demons; he was looking to the Father.

00:14:57.611 --> 00:15:01.040
His eyes were fixed upon the Lord.

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:04.293
And that was the most amazing part of why I kept looking at him.

00:15:04.293 --> 00:15:14.940
I was like, "Wow, he knows his assignment, but he's waiting for instructions from the Lord as he's watching over my family.

00:15:14.940 --> 00:15:25.360
" And he spoke to me and said, "I'm here on an assignment for you, but I have a word to give you from the Lord.

00:15:25.360 --> 00:15:31.165
" And he spoke and said, "Love never fails.

00:15:31.165 --> 00:15:34.710
" And he said, "Faith works by love.

00:15:34.710 --> 00:15:42.549
" And he said the greater glory what you are looking for is attached to the love walk.

00:15:42.549 --> 00:15:44.859
What have you done with love?

00:15:44.859 --> 00:15:46.750
What did you do with love?

00:15:46.940 --> 00:15:48.559
How do you treat your fellow brother?

00:15:49.519 --> 00:15:50.960
Love never fails.

00:15:51.440 --> 00:15:56.434
First Corinthians 13, going over the love walk—the foundational love.

00:15:58.400 --> 00:15:58.800
God is love.

00:15:59.599 --> 00:16:03.440
It's not what he does; it's who he is.

00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:04.640
God is love.

00:16:04.640 --> 00:16:11.920
And as I saw that angel with that opal, and his sword looked like a lightning bolt.

00:16:11.920 --> 00:16:16.720
And where he held it had emeralds.

00:16:25.074 --> 00:16:31.611
He had emeralds inside of that handle that were glowing from the inside out.

00:16:31.611 --> 00:16:39.519
They weren't like light reflecting off of them; the light was coming from within them.

00:16:39.519 --> 00:16:44.840
These beautiful emeralds were green and they were massive.

00:16:44.840 --> 00:16:49.920
And he was holding it, but you could see the green on the side as his hand was on it.

00:16:49.920 --> 00:16:59.120
And I could see these green beautiful stones that had black onyx on the outside of them lining them.

00:17:00.240 --> 00:17:04.319
They were set in black onyx with gold.

00:17:04.319 --> 00:17:06.359
And he was holding the handle.

00:17:06.359 --> 00:17:15.226
And as the handle went up, it had a handguard that protected his hand, like what you would have on a sword that goes out like this to protect your hand.

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:22.720
But there was a lightning bolt—not just any kind of light.

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:27.800
It wasn't like a blade like you would see in a normal sword.

00:17:27.800 --> 00:17:35.440
It was like lightning that was his weapon.

00:17:35.440 --> 00:17:40.089
It was a lightning bolt; it was like electricity was the blade of his sword.

00:17:41.227 --> 00:17:45.440
And he was holding it there, but he was standing with his arms out like this.

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:49.200
He was ready for action.

00:17:50.880 --> 00:17:56.366
Most people get tired if we have our arm held up there, but he doesn't get tired.

00:17:56.366 --> 00:17:59.076
His eyes were fixed upon our Father.

00:17:59.076 --> 00:18:12.811
In the other hand, he had a horn that had a royalty garment, like a royalty flag, hanging off of the horn.

00:18:23.979 --> 00:18:30.960
It was gold-outlined and looked like a W with crimson red mixed with purple and gold, and it was gorgeous the way it was dripping.

00:18:30.960 --> 00:18:36.000
It was fastened to the horn, but he was waiting for instruction.

00:18:36.380 --> 00:18:43.147
But as he came, he said to me, "I've been instructed today.

00:18:43.147 --> 00:18:49.029
I've been assigned to you and your family.

00:18:49.039 --> 00:18:52.960
" There was more to what he said, but that was for us.

00:18:52.960 --> 00:19:04.880
And I'm thankful that God would graciously show us these things.

00:19:05.840 --> 00:19:06.160
Kaleidoscope.

00:19:10.373 --> 00:19:12.400
Thank you.

00:19:12.951 --> 00:19:17.398
You know, Brendan has a hard time with even his own language.

00:19:18.559 --> 00:19:19.263
Gyroscope, Kaleidoscope.

00:19:19.263 --> 00:19:21.520
They sound the same a little bit.

00:19:21.520 --> 00:19:23.387
But all glory to Jesus.

00:19:24.100 --> 00:19:27.712
As we were praying, I kept seeing him, and he was here.

00:19:29.600 --> 00:19:32.640
And then what was the next part?

00:19:34.270 --> 00:19:35.990
Heaven is invading earth.

00:19:35.990 --> 00:19:39.063
Yes, Heaven is invading earth.

00:19:43.253 --> 00:19:43.946
I saw the universe and the stars that were thrown into space.

00:19:43.946 --> 00:19:49.120
But as he was there, I could see it.

00:19:49.120 --> 00:20:01.029
Oh, and then I heard regarding the great Babylon, I saw a storm coming again.

00:20:02.906 --> 00:20:03.760
And he said, "A major storm is coming.

00:20:03.760 --> 00:20:05.223
A major storm is coming.

00:20:11.439 --> 00:20:11.639
" I saw Babylon.

00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:13.940
And most people say, "Well, it's Rome.

00:20:13.940 --> 00:20:16.160
" No, again, it was New York.

00:20:21.268 --> 00:20:21.931
It was referencing New York.

00:20:28.044 --> 00:20:28.276
And that's what I was seeing.

00:20:28.276 --> 00:20:36.480
You say, "Well, the 12 major hills and all that," and people try to argue there.

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:39.600
And if you go to—is his name Brewer?

00:20:40.133 --> 00:20:41.817
He has the YouTube channel.

00:20:43.600 --> 00:20:45.413
He has the beard and he is a Baptist minister.

00:20:45.413 --> 00:20:46.435
Yes, Troy Brewer?

00:20:46.435 --> 00:20:52.423
He teaches end-time stuff a lot and he's on there a lot.

00:20:52.423 --> 00:21:10.760
He even talks about New York being Mystery Babylon and he can prove it; he shows the map and the hills and everything, and it goes alongside it because when you're hearing stuff and you think, "Lord, does this line up with the word?

00:21:10.760 --> 00:21:15.272
" you don't want to go off into flakyville.

00:21:15.272 --> 00:21:17.456
You want to stay grounded.

00:21:17.456 --> 00:21:26.046
Just because you see it doesn't mean it's—you need to make sure it's not flaky.

00:21:26.046 --> 00:21:33.626
But as I was seeing it over, I told D, "It's been glorious.

00:21:33.626 --> 00:21:34.603
" That was wonderful.

00:21:34.603 --> 00:21:38.120
We are so excited about it.

00:21:38.120 --> 00:21:46.240
And then she read Revelation 18 and what the Lord was saying about the Mystery of Babylon.

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:50.091
So I think that was it.

00:21:50.091 --> 00:21:51.919
No, the dragon.

00:21:51.919 --> 00:21:53.208
Oh, I saw a dragon.

00:21:53.208 --> 00:21:54.300
See, Braden, you're awesome.

00:22:01.944 --> 00:22:02.192
I saw the dragon.

00:22:13.520 --> 00:22:13.810
Okay, so I saw a cliff.

00:22:13.810 --> 00:22:17.476
Robert Breaker teaches a lot of cool stuff.

00:22:17.476 --> 00:22:20.871
I'm telling you, that guy's sharp.

00:22:37.011 --> 00:22:37.389
I like to look at his stuff when he has the chart and his little dry-erase board and he does all this stuff.

00:22:53.280 --> 00:22:53.600
I think it's cool, man.

00:23:02.319 --> 00:23:03.253
I get into that.

00:23:03.893 --> 00:23:04.674
It keeps me entertained.

00:23:04.674 --> 00:23:06.799
But he's pretty sharp.

00:23:06.799 --> 00:23:11.240
What was I telling you?

00:23:11.240 --> 00:23:11.520
Dragon.

00:23:11.520 --> 00:23:12.080
Okay.

00:23:12.080 --> 00:23:15.497
The dragon was on the side of this hill.

00:23:18.439 --> 00:23:19.759
And as it opened its mouth, it was in the rocks.

00:23:24.160 --> 00:23:24.480
It was hidden in the rocks this whole time.

00:23:24.480 --> 00:23:28.600
And as it opened its mouth, the rocks became a dragon.

00:23:30.920 --> 00:23:38.456
And it opened its mouth and the water started to come inside of that dragon's mouth.

00:23:38.456 --> 00:23:42.680
And all of a sudden I saw amber—like the tree sap that's hardened.

00:23:43.246 --> 00:23:57.800
It was in a circle and the dragon's claw out of his hand grabbed a hold of that and was holding it, and I saw things moving around in it.

00:23:57.800 --> 00:24:04.520
Now that looked very occultic, like a cult, like satanic.

00:24:07.440 --> 00:24:15.679
And so I thought that was interesting because it was concerning the water.

00:24:24.497 --> 00:24:26.524
It was right after Mystery Babylon and the dragon opened its mouth and the water came out; it was breathing on the water.

00:24:26.524 --> 00:24:32.137
There was something going on with the water and I thought that was interesting.

00:24:32.137 --> 00:24:40.960
I could see the mist and all the stuff rolling around it and I thought, "What in the world?

00:24:58.960 --> 00:24:59.280
" And so maybe that's Wormwood.

00:24:59.600 --> 00:25:01.680
I don't know folks.

00:25:02.640 --> 00:25:11.067
I just tell you what I see and I go, "Hey, that was way out there.

00:25:14.408 --> 00:25:17.770
" But that dragon became alive out of the rocks, opened its mouth, and gobbled up the water out of the ocean.

00:25:29.742 --> 00:25:30.000
And as it came forth out of him, it was steaming.

00:25:34.186 --> 00:25:34.399
It was like it was bubbling.

